<p
                style="margin-bottom: 0px;"
            >In this video, we explore advanced customization of Odoo's search functionality.</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
	<li
                >We focus on creating customized filters and groupings, applicable not only to contacts, but also to items, invoices, and any other section where the search bar is present.</li>
	<li
                >For example, you'll learn how to group contacts by status and create filters to quickly find specific information, such as all contacts based in France or those residing in Pleasant Hill and holding the position of analyst.</li>
	<li
                >This customization allows you to fully exploit the power of Odoo's search tool for greater efficiency.</li>
</ul>
